<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٨٢ -<span class="c5"> بَاب:</span> مَنْ قَسَمَ الْغَنِيمَةَ فِي غَزْوِهِ وَسَفَرِهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ رَافِعٌ:</span> كُنَّا مَعَ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> بِذِي الْحُلَيْفَةِ، فَأَصَبْنَا غَنَمًا وَإِبِلًا، فَعَدَلَ عَشَرَةً مِنَ الْغَنَمِ بِبَعِيرٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٢٣٥٦]</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>